installationInstructions.title: door insert all scatched up
installationInstructions.content: Took me a while to figure out that the bottom plastic strip is all that holds in the panel.  Once it is removed , it pulls out easily       When the new panel arrived,just slide it up into the top grooove, and push the bottom strip back into its groove.    The front looks like new!
